Package com.douglasjose.tech.csv

Interface Summary
Csv Data structure to represent a CSV (comma separated values) file as a matrix in memory.
CsvParser The CsvParser class contains the functionality required to persist the Csv data structure.
 

Class Summary
AbstractCsvParser Skeleton interface class which provides a general CsvParser implementation.
BasicCsv Simple implementation of the Csv interface.
CsvFactory Utility class used to create Csv implementations based in a specific format.
OfficeCsvParser Microsoft Office/OpenOffice compatible Csv implementation.
